<mixertitle>GAP package NormalizInterface</mixertitle>

<h2>GAP wrapper for Normaliz</h2>
<p class="homelink">[<a href="https://gap-packages.github.io/NormalizInterface">WWW homepage</a>]</p>
<h4>Authors</h4>
<p><a href="http://wwwb.math.rwth-aachen.de/~gutsche/">Sebastian Gutsche</a>, 
<a href="http://www.quendi.de/math">Max Horn</a>, 
<a href="https://www.normaliz.uni-osnabrueck.de">Christof Söger</a></p>
<h4>Short Description</h4>
<p><![CDATA[The <span class='pkgname'>NormalizInterface</span> package provides  a GAP interface to <a href='http://www.home.uni-osnabrueck.de/wbruns/normaliz/'>Normaliz</a>,  enabling direct access to the complete functionality of Normaliz, such as  computations in affine monoids, vector configurations, lattice polytopes, and rational cones.  ]]>
</p>

<mixer part="extra" needed="no"/>

